sentence: ¿Qué estado americano fué el último en ser admitido?
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dct:subject dbc:States_of_the_United_States ; <http://dbpedia.org/property/admittancedate> ?x } ORDER BY DESC(?x) LIMIT 1
sparqlQald:
SELECT ?stateLabel
WHERE {
  ?state rdf:type dbo:State .
  ?state dbo:admittedDate ?date .
  
  FILTER NOT EXISTS {
    ?state2 rdf:type dbo:State .
    ?state2 dbo:admittedDate ?date2 .
    ?date2 > ?date .
  }
  
  ?state rdfs:label ?stateLabel .
  FILTER(LANG(?stateLabel) = "es")
}
ORDER BY ASC(?date)
LIMIT 1

sentence: ¿En qué estudio grabaron los Beatles su primer album?
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX db: <http://dbpedia.org/> SELECT ?studio WHERE { ?album dbo:artist dbr:The_Beatles ; rdf:type dbo:Album ; dbo:releaseDate ?date ; dbp:studio ?studio } ORDER BY ASC(?date) LIMIT 1
sparqlQald:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
SELECT ?studio
WHERE {
  ?beatles dbo:artist dbpedia:The_Beatles.
  ?beatles dbo:associatedMusicalArtist ?associatedArtist.
  ?associatedArtist dbo:associatedBand ?band.
  ?band dbo:background dbpedia:The_Beatles.
  ?album dbo:artist ?associatedArtist.
  ?album dbo:recordedIn ?studio.
  ?album dbo:genre ?genre.
  FILTER(CONTAINS(LCASE(STR(?genre)), "rock")).
}
LIMIT 1
